   ```

4. **Access the application:**
   - Frontend: http://localhost:3000
   - Backend API: http://localhost:8080

## Features

- âœ¨ AI-powered documentation generation
- ðŸ“ Complete project scaffolding
- ðŸ”„ GitHub repository creation
